description: Delight your taste buds with a mash up of Caribbean and Southeast Asian flavors. Caribbean Fusion Sandwiches use exotic ingredients such as Cuban spiced pork belly, Papa Bois dry rub jerk chicken, and pork marinated in coconut milk and lemongrass.  All sandwiches include Caribbean Slaw, Papa Mayo, Caramelized onion, tamarind sauce and are served on a freshly baked French Baguette. Our sides include Mango Salsa, Black Bean Corn Salsa, Pistachio Rice, and Spicy Green Papaya Salad. And you can cleanse your palate with Papa Bois' Lychee Lemonade and Lavender Cucumber Limeade.
name: Papa Bois
